<div class="min-h-screen bg-cover bg-center flex items-center"
     style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path("food1.png") %>');">
<section class="py-0 w-full pt-10">
  <div class="flex justify-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4">
      <h1 class="text-7xl sm:text-8xl font-bold text-gray-900 drop-shadow-lg">
        <span>C</span>
        <span class="-mx-4 text-5xl sm:text-6xl">🍙</span>
        <span>lorie Ba</span>
        <span class="-mx-4 text-5xl sm:text-6xl">🍞</span>
        <span>k</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600">
        我慢の記録ではなく、工夫の記録。
